Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:52.95,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Do you know？　身の程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:55.99,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yes, I know！　高いプライド
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:58.87,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What you want？　言いなさいよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:01.33,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}All I want！Only you！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:05.12,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,どんなやり込み要素を盛り込んでいても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:08.09,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,思い込みが過ぎてるでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.09,0:01:11.13,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,こうじゃないと言いたいハッピーエンド
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.76,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}意味不明の世迷い言を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:17.09,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}空想だった感情が現実に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:19.60,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Ah！Cool！ You’re cool！Beautiful！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:23.31,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}平穏だった日常が乱雑に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:25.60,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I can’t believe！ You have to leave！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:27.65,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,10)\fad(200,200)}好きも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:27.65,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1440,10)\fad(200,200)}嫌いも
